gameengine.model

Interface IAction

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Action, ChangeAttribute, Destroy, GlideLeft, GlideRight, GlideUp, GlidingAction, HarmEnemy, HorizontalBounceCollision, HorizontalStaticCollision, LoseGame, MoveDown, MoveLeft, MoveRight, MoveUp, MovingAction, NextLevel, UpdateActor, VerticalBounceCollision, VerticalStaticCollision, WinGame

    public interface IAction
    This interface defines the public methods that each Action subclass will have. We want to keep our Actions modular so that any Action can be used in the place of any other. This will make it easier to define the behaviors for any Actor object.
    Author:
    blakekaplan

      Performs a specific procedure which will be specific to each Action subclass
